05:09.000 --> 05:13.920
in real time to people who can't participate because you know it's a kernel development

05:13.920 --> 05:18.440
conference we get people who want to come from all over the globe and we always have

05:18.440 --> 05:22.560
corners of the globe especially when we run the conference in America that even if they

05:22.560 --> 05:26.240
have the best will in the world and they can actually scrape up the money to come they're

05:26.240 --> 05:33.560
often denied visas by the US authorities so it can be a real really difficult problem.

05:33.560 --> 05:38.880
